fence of the Church against the State. Since the later Middle Ages <i>Hugh</i> has also been used as an Anglicized form of the Gaelic name Aodh ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Hugh Filiol was born in 1280 as the son of William Filiol. He married Mrs Hugh Filiol before 1310, in Europe. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1280–":"1280–Surnud","1280–Male":"1280–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1310–Male":"1310–Surnud","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","before 1310":"enne 1310","1310":"1310","1250":"1250","1280":"1280","Europe":"Europe","Dorsetshire, England":"Dorset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1280–":"1280–Kuollut","1280–Male":"1280–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1310–Male":"1310–Kuollut","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","before 1310":"ennen vuotta 1310","1310":"1310","1250":"1250","1280":"1280","Europe":"Europe","Dorsetshire, England":"Dorset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1280–":"1280–Décédé","1280–Male":"1280–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1310–Male":"1310–Décédé","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","before 1310":"avant 1310","1310":"1310","1250":"1250","1280":"1280","Europe":"Europe","Dorsetshire, England":"Dorset, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Hugh Filiol est né en 1280, fils de William Filiol. Il a épousé Mrs Hugh Filiol avant 1310, à Europe. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1280–":"1280–Verstorben","1280–Male":"1280–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1310–Male":"1310–Verstorben","1250–Male":"1250–Verstorben","before 1310":"vor 1310","1310":"1310","1250":"1250","1280":"1280","Europe":"Europa","Dorsetshire, England":"Dorset, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Hugh Filiol wurde 1280, als Sohn von William Filiol geboren. Er hat vor 1310 in Europa Mrs Hugh Filiol geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1280–":"1280–Desede","1280–Male":"1280–Desede","–Female":"Desede","1310–Male":"1310–Desede","1250–Male":"1250–Desede","before 1310":"before 1310","1310":"1310","1250":"1250","1280":"1280","Europe":"Europe","Dorsetshire, England":"D